author: Hopethepirate
title: Locked out with no explanation
text: Despite having two-factor authentication enabled through the Authenticator app, my account was accessed without my authorization last month. I was able to recover it and remove the unwanted logins at that time. Today my account has been randomly locked, with no email, warning, or explanation as to how, why, or how to recover it. What is the point of having 2FA if someone can still access my account without my knowledge? This account contains videos I worked extremely hard on and views that cannot be replaced. Support responses so far have been unhelpful and repetitive, and one even came back with placeholder text (â€œXXXXâ€) instead of real instructions. I am pregnant and already under a lot of stress, and this situation has left me feeling frustrated, upset, and honestly violated. This is a Sellerâ€™s account containing all of my personal information, and to receive absolutely no assistance or even a clear reason for the lock is unacceptable. Please escalate this immediately and provide an actual explanation and recovery path.
